<lb n="0080a23" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0080003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說無量功德陀羅尼經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0080a24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0080a25" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0080004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔西天譯經〕－【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0080004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西天譯經【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】，宋西天譯經【明】</note><app n="0080004"><lem wit="【大】">西天譯經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">宋西天譯經</rdg></app>三藏<note n="0080005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（朝散…臣）十三字＝（法師）二字【宋】【元】</note><note n="0080005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（朝散…臣）十三字【大】，法師【宋】【元】</note><app cb:word-count="13" n="0080005"><lem wit="【大】">朝散大夫試光
<lb n="0080a26" ed="T"/>祿卿明教大師臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">法師</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0080a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0080a2701">爾時世尊告阿難言。汝當諦聽我今為汝及
<lb n="0080a28" ed="T"/>末法眾生。宣說無量功德陀羅尼。汝當憶念
<lb n="0080a29" ed="T"/>勿得忘失。使<note n="0080006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">於＝于【明】＊</note><note n="0080006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】＊，于【明】＊</note><app n="0080006"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">于</rdg></app>當來濁惡世中。與諸眾生作
<pb n="0080b" xml:id="T19.0934.0080b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0080b01" ed="T"/>大善利。阿難若有眾生得聞此陀羅尼。每日
<lb n="0080b02" ed="T"/>晨朝誦二十一遍。是人<app type="star" corresp="#0080006"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">于</rdg></app>千劫中所積惡業
<lb n="0080b03" ed="T"/>悉皆消滅。見身獲得安隱快樂。若人<note n="0080007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">志＝至【元】【明】</note><note n="0080007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">志【大】，至【元】【明】</note><app n="0080007"><lem wit="【大】">志</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">至</rdg></app>心持
<lb n="0080b04" ed="T"/>誦一洛叉數。是人當來得見慈氏菩薩。若持
<lb n="0080b05" ed="T"/>誦二洛叉數。當來得見觀自在菩薩。若持誦
<lb n="0080b06" ed="T"/>三洛叉數。當來得見無量壽佛。即說陀羅尼
<lb n="0080b07" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0080b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0080b0801" cb:type="dharani">那謨<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note>那莫阿<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0080b09" ed="T"/>哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>阿彌多<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0080008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＝媻【明】＊</note><note n="0080008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆【大】＊，媻【明】＊</note><app n="0080008"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">媻</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">二</note>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>誐多<note place="inline">引</note>野
<lb n="0080b10" ed="T"/><note place="inline">三</note>阿囉曷<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>三藐訖三<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">四</note>怛
<lb n="0080b11" ed="T"/><g ref="#CB00853"/>他<note place="inline">引五</note>阿彌帝<note place="inline">引六</note>阿彌覩<note place="inline">引</note>訥<app type="star" corresp="#0080008"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">媻</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>味
<lb n="0080b12" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引七</note>阿彌多三<app type="star" corresp="#0080008"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">媻</rdg></app>味<note place="inline">八</note>阿彌多尾訖蘭<note place="inline">二合引</note>帝
<lb n="0080b13" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引九</note>阿彌多尾訖蘭<note place="inline">二合引</note>多誐<note place="inline">引</note>彌儞<note place="inline">十</note>誐誐
<lb n="0080b14" ed="T"/>那計<note place="inline">引</note>哩底<note place="inline">二合</note>羯哩<note place="inline">引十一</note>薩哩嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>訖梨
<lb n="0080b15" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>舍<note place="inline">十二</note>剎煬羯哩<note place="inline">二合</note>曳<note place="inline">引</note>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十
<lb n="0080b16" ed="T"/>三</note></p>
<lb n="0080b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0080b1701">爾時阿難。得聞如來說是無量功德陀羅尼
<lb n="0080b18" ed="T"/>已。歡喜信受禮佛而退。</p>
<lb n="0080b19" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說無量功德陀羅尼經</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
